il_skeleton <- il_counties %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = il_counties) 


#leaflet package

il <- leaflet(il_counties) %>%
  setView(lng = -89.3985, lat = 40.6331, zoom = 8) %>% 
  addProviderTiles("OpenStreetMap.BlackAndWhite") %>%  
  addPolygons(color = "black", weight = 1, fillOpacity = 0)

il
